## 👋 About Me

> *"Building AI-powered platforms that scale to billions — from strategy to execution."*

I'm a **Global Product & AI Executive** with **20+ years** of experience leading strategy, build, and scale of enterprise and consumer platforms. Currently **Global Director of Product Management at Uber**, owning Customer Experience, Support, and Autonomous Operations platforms powering **10B+ transactions annually** across **70+ countries**.

- 🚀 **AI-Led Transformation** — GenAI, Agentic AI, MCP, ML, LLMs, Voice & Visual AI
- 💡 **Platform Scale** — Architected platforms supporting 1B+ annual transactions
- 💰 **Business Impact** — $100M+ cost savings | $10B+ GB unlocked
- 🌍 **Global Reach** — Led 200+ member cross-functional teams across 70+ countries
- 🎤 **Thought Leader** — Speaker at Google, NASSCOM, Women in Product, LinkedIn

---

## 🏢 Experience

### 🔵 Uber Inc. — *Global Director, Product Management* `Apr 2024 – Present`
> Bangalore | Reported to Senior Director

- Own global product strategy for Customer Experience, Support & Autonomous Operations — **1B+ annual transactions**, 20+ products, 70+ countries, 50+ languages
- Led GenAI & Agentic AI transformation delivering **$100M+ in cost savings**
- Architecting **Model Context Protocol (MCP)** platform strategy for Uber-wide Agentic AI APIs
- Unlocked **$10B+ in Gross Bookings** through enterprise-grade self-serve & configurability
- Achieved **95% reduction in fraud, abuse & account compromise**
- Built & lead **15-member global product team** + oversight of 200+ cross-functional members

### 🟣 Zeotap — *VP, Product Management* `Jun 2021 – Apr 2024`
> Bangalore | Reported to CPO

- Drove **$50M ARR** and **10x growth in 2 years** for AI-driven Customer Data & Audience platform
- Architected cloud platform strategy across data ingestion, identity resolution, segmentation & activation
- Partnerships with **Google Cloud, AWS, Microsoft Azure** & MarTech platforms
- Ensured compliance with GDPR, HIPAA, TISAX, EU AI Act across 100+ enterprise clients

### 🟠 Bewgle *(Acquired by AccelData)* — *VP, Product, Partnerships & Marketing* `2019 – 2021`
> Bangalore

- Drove **350% revenue growth** and **1,000+ brand adoptions** with AI/NLP omni-channel platform
- Defined monetization strategy — usage-based pricing increased conversion by **22%**
- Represented company at VC pitches, industry forums, and acquirer discussions

### 🔷 AT&T / Thryv — *Lead Product Manager* `2014 – 2018`
> Bay Area, CA

- Directed product strategy for AT&T's local search ad platform generating **$350M annual revenue**
- Increased native fill rates by **150%**, expanded inventory by **60%+** via publisher partnerships

### 🔹 TiVo, 24-7.ai, Fidelity & Y Combinator Startups `2004 – 2014`
> Bay Area & Boston

- Built enterprise CX & analytics platforms processing **100M+ daily transactions**
- Designed wealth management platforms handling **$1T+ in transactional value**
- Boosted eCommerce order value by **24%** via NLP-powered personalization engines

